                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>Pero neh nikchi:waya se: *lucha porque..., antes** nika:n Tozán pos no: yetok n' *escuelita**, tikchihchi:wkah *de cartÃ³n**.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
            </ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION>
